    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142050/extras/c0987c0007a77c023a74f22e20e3aa64.avif?t=1771525643\" width=1560 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the creative director of Eternal Darkness and Legacy of Kain, Denis Dyack returns once more.<br><br>Deadhaus Sonata is a third-person narrative-driven action RPG where you play as the undead battling the living, growing in power, and exploring an ocean of content.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into Malorum, a dark and crumbling world where the lines between life and death no longer hold. Deadhaus Sonata invites you to embrace the undead, master supernatural powers, and carve your place within a realm shaped by ancient forces, political intrigue, and the choices of its players. Play alone or join up to six players in cooperative play as you face the living and uncover the secrets that shape this fallen realm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142050/extras/6c2006c9610b7d645fd2389c6e62b671.avif?t=1771525643\" width=1560 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142050/extras/7b60941c7d7c81c4ee4a2bb51b9c8416.poster.avif?t=1771525643\" width=1170 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142050/extras/7b60941c7d7c81c4ee4a2bb51b9c8416.webm?t=1771525643\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142050/extras/7b60941c7d7c81c4ee4a2bb51b9c8416.mp4?t=1771525643\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become the undead and step into the iconic role of the Vampire. Feed on the living to grow stronger, unlock supernatural abilities, and evolve through a progression path built around dominance and mastery. Other undead forms wait in the dark, ready to be revealed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142050/extras/67b39b8348aa03799300f57523b17d9d.avif?t=1771525643\" width=1560 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142050/extras/aa7e48e4d452da05fc8357fb37e09dd4.poster.avif?t=1771525643\" width=1170 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142050/extras/aa7e48e4d452da05fc8357fb37e09dd4.webm?t=1771525643\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142050/extras/aa7e48e4d452da05fc8357fb37e09dd4.mp4?t=1771525643\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a land shattered by divine war and corruption. Malorum is filled with haunted fortresses, forgotten kingdoms, and ruins shaped by ancient history. Every discovery reveals new layers of lore where nothing is ever as it first appears.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142050/extras/1358eaf81cf1652dc9901d1f36d35728.avif?t=1771525643\" width=1560 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142050/extras/2a7cbcb66869d5f3b1e25fa4c7deba09.poster.avif?t=1771525643\" width=1170 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142050/extras/2a7cbcb66869d5f3b1e25fa4c7deba09.webm?t=1771525643\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142050/extras/2a7cbcb66869d5f3b1e25fa4c7deba09.mp4?t=1771525643\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Harness supernatural mobility, strike with precision, and unleash abilities that reward timing, positioning, and clever decision-making. Your undead form is your greatest weapon, and more forms will emerge as your power grows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142050/extras/6d28bf6c48eab09839fd8d0882e634c3.avif?t=1771525643\" width=1560 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142050/extras/6457582e1c22a6c38ef9614efb55c009.poster.avif?t=1771525643\" width=1170 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142050/extras/6457582e1c22a6c38ef9614efb55c009.webm?t=1771525643\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142050/extras/6457582e1c22a6c38ef9614efb55c009.mp4?t=1771525643\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deadhaus Sonata features a tarot-based skill system where every card represents arcane power shaped by Malorum’s forgotten history. Cards are earned through quests, battles, and exploration, and each one unlocks new abilities that can be mixed, matched, and upgraded.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build for precision, raw power, mobility, tanking, or supernatural control. The tarot system gives you endless ways to refine your build and unleash devastating forces against the living.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142050/extras/028b255b77b7658538f8a162410aec5b.avif?t=1771525643\" width=1560 height=160 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142050/extras/bef43ca6dfc0da09d770511979059941.poster.avif?t=1771525643\" width=1170 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142050/extras/bef43ca6dfc0da09d770511979059941.webm?t=1771525643\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142050/extras/bef43ca6dfc0da09d770511979059941.mp4?t=1771525643\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Loot in Deadhaus Sonata is earned through feats that track your actions, history, and performance, not random drops. Every item is shaped by what you do.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gear, artifacts, legendary items, and tarot cards all tie into Malorum’s supernatural and political history. Playing is crafting, and your past becomes a resource that influences your future.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142050/extras/34615a4fb57644e965e6dc9f1b7b0666.avif?t=1771525643\" width=1560 height=160 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142050/extras/9a0c6215a8310ab54561c519c1788422.poster.avif?t=1771525643\" width=1170 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142050/extras/9a0c6215a8310ab54561c519c1788422.webm?t=1771525643\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1142050/extras/9a0c6215a8310ab54561c519c1788422.mp4?t=1771525643\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deadhaus Sonata is a story-driven experience, featuring more than 15 hours of professionally voiced narration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Created by Denis Dyack, known for his work on Eternal Darkness: Sanity’s Requiem, Blood Omen: Legacy of Kain, and Too Human, Deadhaus Sonata is a new dark fantasy world shaped by psychological depth, interconnected lore, and player-driven consequence. Every choice leaves a mark on your character and the world around you, with sentient gear, persistent events, and outcomes shaped by time, place, and action.</p>",
